{"tid":1600651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你無本地以外followers, retweet都只係圍爐!","createTime":"2019-09-28T16:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T07:26:02.000Z","uid":104902,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56b51116fc854042406b9395bcff4e0436bf4175","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"你無本地以外followers, retweet都只係圍爐!<br />\n<br />\nRetweet只係圍爐!<br />\n<br />\n多搵呢啲國際大媒新聞或知名人物tweet入去留言。加返啲相片、影片或者其他新聞嘅link。見到自己友留言，有價值就like（唔好喪like留言，唔使retweet留言）。再rt原po。<br />\n<br />\n要學五毛！五毛都唔會喺自己度retweet, 係專出去人哋度留言㗎嘛。<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/goofrider/status/1170088696109862912?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgoofrider%2Fstatus%2F1170088696109862912%3Fs%3D12&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8r8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=d5e5d1ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgoofrider%2Fstatus%2F1170088696109862912%3Fs%3D12&h=c46e9390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/goofrider/status/1170088696109862912?s=12</a><br />\n<br />\n註: Solomon Yue同原文作者係twitter有不斷交流，可見其論之說服力<br />\n<br />\n同我推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2237fee2f83b3e39ccb13b865cb92bfb3aa8667","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"當然最好係正正經經用自己語言講返自己嘅感受。一係貼返啲其他可靠來源嘅新聞link(@hongkongfp, @rthk_enews, @nytimes<br />\n等)。其次就用影片、相片。<br />\n<br />\n唔係bot咁炸文宣。同埋唔好離題。咁會令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n本地文宣係攞文宣組嘅作品盲目瘋傳就得。<br />\n<br />\n網軍，係要攻㗎。"},{"pid":"0bb746f981ecda6367c3d11aa67f155d3b1b9b60","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"重申： 要搵有關香港、中國、台灣、外交、貿易之類嘅tweet先好留言。唔好離題，唔好騎劫。<br />\n<br />\n真係要離題入去唔關港中台事嘅tweet度留言, 就要好卑微咁話希望人哋關心下我哋。不過可免則免。"},{"pid":"a853d33aa8c1a7b829b978ba6160d027387e6987","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"呢個只係對新手嘅建議。你同外國交流得夠多，慢慢就知道點樣將人哋嘅議題同香港嘅問題拉埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n重點係交流，唔係單方向盲推。人哋講緊啲乜你要回應下。Show that u listen and care about what they say.<br />\n<br />\n你盲推、盲谷rt/like，咁一切對你只係個數字。交流，係講人心。"},{"pid":"ea6daed8cde149e045858db2ae09d691d07760a3","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"記得retweet原Po! 咁其他手足先多啲機會見到個po。<br />\n<br />\n見到自己友rt外國、圈外嘅tweet就要識做, 入去留言同like其他自己友嘅留言。做完又一樣要retweet原po。<br />\n<br />\n鐘意嘅可以retweet埋自己及其他自己友嘅留言，等多啲其他自己芨睇到like到。有需要、有價值嘅留言咪retweet囉，唔使個個都rt。順其自然就得。"},{"pid":"1c9a254425334239a5f7a9b352663c3361fbc55f","tid":1600651,"uid":321622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c7e035770d3911823a1f5fe824c0e653d79f6a","tid":1600651,"uid":321622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"929 超巨大連儂牆 將出現係遊行隊伍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac897d8eee5b5b6205e42aaae8110ff58d86fcd","tid":1600651,"uid":321622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6eb1d73a55b05a5bcafd55961ae2ede9cdae8f","tid":1600651,"uid":257293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"推唔到都回下先<br />\n大家真係未識玩Twitter"},{"pid":"7dac7aca3a1a1275afda04f37bd9fed045af383b","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73540fd11a1775e7d3929930d6576cd49cb1c95","tid":1600651,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"puah"},{"pid":"63bf03a396550090a537fdd5ea35d9cafbc84849","tid":1600651,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"全人類去twitter做文宣!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n#929GlobalAntiTotalitarian or類似tag<br />\n<br />\n始終香港人少玩"},{"pid":"1ab829e6e5b4e55b1d9b837ce75f926dd57ea733","tid":1600651,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T19:24:46.000Z","msg":"講得啱！有twitter跟住做！無twitter嗱嗱聲開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f7fba47964082bc4196411962bc7722253a355","tid":1600651,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T07:26:02.000Z","msg":"自推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}